title: The Eye of Cthulhu
info: The Eye of Cthulhu is a Hardmode, post-Plantera Yoyo which has a 33.33% / 55.56% chance to drop from Mothron during a Solar Eclipse. It is one of the few yoyos that can stay in the air indefinitely, and it has a reach of 23 tiles. It is currently the second strongest yoyo in the game, only beaten by the Terrarian.
